{"id":"int-678d64907c046ec2d61233b5d2ee8964","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-06-12T14:08:58.490361299Z","actor":"Hans Kohlreiter","issue_id":"at-zib.2.5","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"open","reason":"Decision: keep the partition open-vs-closed only; no parked/ partition. Deferred/long-parked issues stay hot. Recorded in ARCHITECTURE-SPEC 'Hot/cold separation'. Hot scan is O(open) ~13us/file — degrades gracefully; status-based routing not worth the complexity."}}
